      &lt;img alt="The Flic logo - script text reading “flic” on the left and a large black circle on the right." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/gMDHwi4Q8EBeb9T9X0BU8Kay30o=/0x42:2050x1409/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73565920/Flic_Logo.0.png" /&gt;
